        options: ["Continue antibiotics for a total of 14 days to prevent recurrence","Discontinue antibiotics based on adequate source control, clinical improvement, and procalcitonin decline","Switch to a broader-spectrum carbapenem to ensure complete bacterial eradication","Obtain repeat CT scan before any changes to antibiotic therapy"],
